  "_meta": {
    "description": "India strategic-import dependency graph. Nodes are causes, commodities, Indian sectors, and macro variables. Edges carry a transmission weight (0-1), a mechanism string, and a lag in days. The cascade engine does a weighted BFS from any cause node and reports every India-side node it reaches.",
    "weightSemantics": "weight = fraction of the upstream shock that propagates along this edge. Multiplied across hops with per-hop decay.",
